        "subject": "LU-4442 tests: add version check for replay-vbr.sh test_7g",
        "message": "LU-4442 tests: add version check for replay-vbr.sh test_7g\n\nIn replay-vbr.sh test_7g.3, because mdt_object_exists() was added\nin http://review.whamcloud.com/9213, client will not be evicted\nwithout object version check.\n\nThe patch also fixes the wrong usage of wait_mds_ost_sync() in\nreplay_vbr.sh test_7_cycle(). The first parameter should be a timeout\nin seconds, not a facet.\n\nThe patch is back-ported from the following ones:\nLustre-commit: 8466731d0834e9d33d4093681d5aa7e4e4368fed\nLustre-change: http://review.whamcloud.com/8973\nand\nLustre-commit: 4eaa2c1b6eaac589ca77627b403347e4223a4c80\nLustre-change: http://review.whamcloud.com/8796\n\nTest-Parameters: envdefinitions=SLOW=yes,ONLY=7 \\\nossdistro=el6 mdsdistro=el6 testlist=replay-vbr\nTest-Parameters: envdefinitions=SLOW=yes,ONLY=7 \\\nossdistro=el6 mdsdistro=el6 \\\nossjob=lustre-b2_5 mdsjob=lustre-b2_5 \\\nossbuildno=42 mdsbuildno=42 testlist=replay-vbr\n\nSigned-off-by: Jian Yu <jian.yu@intel.com>\nChange-Id: If3418f64442f7e531b860fe671b9ca1ed97ca33e\n"
      },
